## into() function

Adds elements from `src` iterable to `dest` Map or Set.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare function into<K, V>(dest: Map<K, V>, src: Iterable<Pair<K, V>>): Map<K, V>;
```

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  dest | <code>Map&lt;K, V&gt;</code> | target collection |
|  src | <code>Iterable&lt;Pair&lt;K, V&gt;&gt;</code> | source collection |
